  <body>
    <div style="basic">
        <p begin="00:00:00.000" end="00:00:04.660" tts:direction="ltr">Hello, visitors. You have arrived at your
<br />final base camp,</p>
        <p begin="00:00:04.660" end="00:00:06.760" tts:direction="ltr">and that is all about story.</p>
        <p begin="00:00:06.760" end="00:00:08.940" tts:direction="ltr">Remember at the beginning of this course,</p>
        <p begin="00:00:08.940" end="00:00:12.100" tts:direction="ltr">I indicated that storytelling is one of
<br />the skills that is</p>
        <p begin="00:00:12.100" end="00:00:15.520" tts:direction="ltr">most important in business analyst
<br />position.</p>
        <p begin="00:00:15.520" end="00:00:18.600" tts:direction="ltr">When we can be able to tell story using
<br />data,</p>
        <p begin="00:00:18.600" end="00:00:23.680" tts:direction="ltr">we are able to give new life to that data
<br />and give new purpose.</p>
        <p begin="00:00:23.680" end="00:00:26.200" tts:direction="ltr">When it comes to your amazing journey,</p>
        <p begin="00:00:26.200" end="00:00:28.640" tts:direction="ltr">you're getting closer and closer to the
<br />end.</p>
        <p begin="00:00:28.640" end="00:00:32.840" tts:direction="ltr">You have see. Taken a spin.</p>
        <p begin="00:00:32.840" end="00:00:34.980" tts:direction="ltr">You have traversed a River.</p>
        <p begin="00:00:34.980" end="00:00:37.320" tts:direction="ltr">You have hit several base cams,</p>
        <p begin="00:00:37.320" end="00:00:41.040" tts:direction="ltr">and finally, you are here at number four.</p>
        <p begin="00:00:41.040" end="00:00:44.560" tts:direction="ltr">You have tremendously progressed through
<br />this course.</p>
        <p begin="00:00:44.560" end="00:00:48.295" tts:direction="ltr">Now let's finish off strong by learning
<br />more about story.</p>
        <p begin="00:00:48.295" end="00:00:51.910" tts:direction="ltr">In this base camp, you'll do these three
<br />activities,</p>
        <p begin="00:00:51.910" end="00:00:53.550" tts:direction="ltr">you'll learn more about story.</p>
        <p begin="00:00:53.550" end="00:00:56.330" tts:direction="ltr">You'll have a chance to do your last data
<br />talk,</p>
        <p begin="00:00:56.330" end="00:00:58.410" tts:direction="ltr">and of course, your final challenge.</p>
        <p begin="00:00:58.410" end="00:01:01.670" tts:direction="ltr">This challenge is very similar to what
<br />your project will look like,</p>
        <p begin="00:01:01.670" end="00:01:05.270" tts:direction="ltr">and it's a good practice to tee up your
<br />skills so that you can</p>
        <p begin="00:01:05.270" end="00:01:10.490" tts:direction="ltr">do a portfolio project worthy of showing
<br />future employers.</p>
        <p begin="00:01:10.490" end="00:01:12.610" tts:direction="ltr">When it comes to the objectives,</p>
        <p begin="00:01:12.610" end="00:01:16.510" tts:direction="ltr">we want to make sure that you're able to
<br />tell impactful data stories,</p>
        <p begin="00:01:16.510" end="00:01:19.370" tts:direction="ltr">that you're formulating narratives that
<br />convey</p>
        <p begin="00:01:19.370" end="00:01:22.820" tts:direction="ltr">insights that come from data We also want
<br />you to</p>
        <p begin="00:01:22.820" end="00:01:25.520" tts:direction="ltr">evaluate the persuasive impact of</p>
        <p begin="00:01:25.520" end="00:01:29.740" tts:direction="ltr">storytelling and have that beginning
<br />middle and end.</p>
        <p begin="00:01:29.740" end="00:01:31.260" tts:direction="ltr">We want you to construct</p>
        <p begin="00:01:31.260" end="00:01:34.940" tts:direction="ltr">those compelling narratives that are
<br />tailored to the specific audience,</p>
        <p begin="00:01:34.940" end="00:01:37.100" tts:direction="ltr">their preferences and objectives.</p>
        <p begin="00:01:37.100" end="00:01:39.840" tts:direction="ltr">Then we want you to make sure that you are
<br />using</p>
        <p begin="00:01:39.840" end="00:01:42.740" tts:direction="ltr">the power of takeaway titles and tooltips.</p>
        <p begin="00:01:42.740" end="00:01:45.160" tts:direction="ltr">That is crossing your Ts.</p>
        <p begin="00:01:45.160" end="00:01:48.060" tts:direction="ltr">So much to learn and to cover and to
<br />apply.</p>
        <p begin="00:01:48.060" end="00:01:50.640" tts:direction="ltr">That's the important part of this course
<br />is that</p>
        <p begin="00:01:50.640" end="00:01:53.610" tts:direction="ltr">we're learning concepts that may not be
<br />revolutionary.</p>
        <p begin="00:01:53.610" end="00:01:55.760" tts:direction="ltr">You're learning to apply them time and</p>
        <p begin="00:01:55.760" end="00:01:58.140" tts:direction="ltr">time again so that when you exit this
<br />course,</p>
        <p begin="00:01:58.140" end="00:02:03.480" tts:direction="ltr">the goal is that you can confidently and
<br />successfully be someone who uses</p>
        <p begin="00:02:03.480" end="00:02:10.140" tts:direction="ltr">data in a meaningful way and convey that
<br />to your audiences. Happy visit.</p>
    </div>
